e.g. using a FutureResult

FutureResult future = new FutureResult();
foo.addListener(new Listener(){
    public void eventOccurred(Event event){
      future.set(event);
    }
  });

foo.doSomethingThatWillFireEventsOnAnotherThread();

assertEquals(expectedEvent, future.get());   // future.get() will block 
until the result is available

 -Neil

